From e634e92ec48f7da142e4bdbc33305c197b3f00b3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harsh Kumar Bijlani <hbijlani@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Jun 2025 20:06:07 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] QSDK: DP: wifi: ath12k: Tx Enqueue Optimization

In the API ath12k_wifi7_dp_tx_send(), directly enqueue the pkts into
the HW if the fast_xmit flag is set in the skb.

This change results in KPI and CPU load improvements.

Signed-off-by: Harsh Kumar Bijlani <hbijlani@qti.qualcomm.com>
